title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell.
description: When trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown. The issue occurs while executing the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' method.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data in a table inside a grid cell.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the data should be successfully exported.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a grid. 
2. Attempt to export data in two tables.
